# the-operator repo: whitelist gitignore.
# Ignore everything in the workspace by default, then re-include only what ships.
# Workspace scratch stays local-only: test-run copies, specs/plans, answer keys, tmp,
# PDFs, screenshots, governance, MCP artifacts.

/*

# Re-include only the shipped pieces
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/builtbybas-intake-operator/
!/showcase/

# Inside the operator: the blind evaluation suite is local-only.
# samples/ ships (the three "Try it" demos); test-inputs/ (the held eval prompts) does not.
/builtbybas-intake-operator/test-inputs/

# Safety: never track OS/editor cruft if it appears inside the included folders
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/.playwright-mcp/
